  "texts": [
    "Another specific challenge in gustatory analysis is effectively capturing consumer hedonic responses and preference data.",
    "These responses are inherently subjective and often difficult to quantify.",
    "While traditional sensory panels provide valuable data, they come with 1 3 limitations, including high costs, small sample sizes, and logistical complexities.",
    "To address these constraints, researchers are exploring alternative methods.",
    "Options include crowdsourcing, mobile app-based feedback systems, and wearable biosensors (Zhao et al. 2024)."
  ]
}